sentences: Steve Hart (born 29 February 1972 in London) is an English pop singer and actor.

As well as the official Worlds Apart magazine and numerous unofficial magazines, there was a Steve Hart magazine called Steve sold in newsagents after he was voted Sexiest Man in Europe for three years running.
He has also written songs for movies, TV shows, and numerous hits for other artists and recently wrote the song for the winner of The Voice UK 2016.
